**来源**（冲突时以 react.dev 为准）：

| 用途 | 站点 | 入口 |
|------|------|------|
| React 19 新 API 参考 | React Reference | https://react.dev/reference/react |
| React DOM / 表单 API | React DOM | https://react.dev/reference/react-dom |
| 发布说明 | React Blog | https://react.dev/blog/2024/12/05/react-19 |
| 18→19 升级 | Upgrade Guide | https://react.dev/blog/2024/04/25/react-19-upgrade-guide |

